 thick), which seperates two conducting/superconducting films.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The exeriment will involve the measurement of the tunneling current from
 one film to the other as the potential between them is increased.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
-in any tunneling process the total energy must be conserved
\end_layout

